{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8bc90446ce","title":"贾正玉的审讯记录","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a39b662864","index":0,"year":1969,"month":11,"day":5,"articleId":"8bc90446ce"}],"tags":[{"id":"3aaab89c2a","name":"刘少奇","type":"人物"},{"id":"44b4a39710","name":"林彪","type":"人物"},{"id":"5f4cf2fdf4","name":"青海文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"82305e518c","name":"江青","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"062c209d4e","name":"贾正玉"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"982982e873","type":"title","text":"贾正玉的审讯记录","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8bc90446ce"},{"id":"26ae0f7058","type":"authors","text":"贾正玉","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8bc90446ce"},{"id":"fe71facb39","type":"paragraph","text":"【贾正玉，男，1937年1月生，青海师范学院政史系毕业生，青海西宁实验小学教师。文革开始，批判会不发言，不写批判文章。69年11月，因支持刘少奇被学校关起来。11月5日被捕。12月2日，正式逮捕。在狱中，贾正玉用筷子绑上破布，蘸上水，在墙上写下“打倒林彪！打倒江青！”“历史宣判我无罪， 有罪的是林彪！”看守给他加上双戒具，钉上几十斤重的脚镣。他几次举起戴着镣铐的手，咬破自己的手指，在墙上写下诗篇：“镣铐叮当响，斗志更昂扬。革命者 怕什么死亡，甘洒热血于牢房！”","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8bc90446ce"},{"id":"c77dc6aee0","type":"paragraph","text":"70年2月12日处死，死前嘴塞棉花，绳勒嘴角。死时33岁。80年（？）中共青海省委和省人民政府分别作出决定，追认他为中国共产党党员，追认他为革命烈士。】","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8bc90446ce"},{"id":"5215a022c0","type":"subtitle","text":"审讯记录：","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8bc90446ce"},{"id":"654d593bb8","type":"paragraph","text":"林彪提出的成绩最大最大最大，损失最小最小最小，是昧着良心说的，搞得别人不敢说话了。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8bc90446ce"},{"id":"05073c342c","type":"paragraph","text":"文化大革命一开始，林彪就把刘少奇同志的权篡夺过去了，林彪是靠吹捧毛主席、靠‘四个伟大’，靠‘大海航行靠舵手、干革命靠的是毛泽东思想’这个口号自己爬上去，把别人挤掉了，采取了一些手段。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8bc90446ce"},{"id":"3a4b2b5ea7","type":"paragraph","text":"多次当着审讯人员的面高呼“打倒林彪！打倒江青！”","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8bc90446ce"},{"id":"52d4143485","type":"paragraph","text":"问：你对无产阶级文化大革命支持吗？","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8bc90446ce"},{"id":"e7e3a6fca8","type":"paragraph","text":"答：我反对，我认为不应该搞，是搞错了，如果说是政变，这实际上是一场政变！","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8bc90446ce"},{"id":"378cdc67a3","type":"paragraph","text":"问：你认为你所说的人民会支持你吗？","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8bc90446ce"},{"id":"65f792ee15","type":"paragraph","text":"答：尽管我没有对人说，但是我相信广大劳动人民在支持我！","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8bc90446ce"},{"id":"d89238f60c","type":"paragraph","text":"问：学校谁支持你？","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8bc90446ce"},{"id":"b3322755ae","type":"paragraph","text":"答：没有。","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8bc90446ce"},{"id":"7d4f0774af","type":"paragraph","text":"问：你们同学谁支持你？","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8bc90446ce"},{"id":"bf0ed7e2b8","type":"paragraph","text":"答：没有。","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8bc90446ce"},{"id":"cfb3956721","type":"paragraph","text":"问：你爱人支持你吗？","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8bc90446ce"},{"id":"7f3f69e7e7","type":"paragraph","text":"答：没有。","index":17,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8bc90446ce"},{"id":"7765535a99","type":"paragraph","text":"问：你认为谁支持你？","index":18,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8bc90446ce"},{"id":"444bb03181","type":"paragraph","text":"答：当革命火焰点燃时，劳动人民会起来支持我的！","index":19,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8bc90446ce"},{"id":"21b0b425ff","type":"paragraph","text":"问：你敢把你说的写下来吗？","index":20,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8bc90446ce"},{"id":"79c732bef1","type":"paragraph","text":"答：敢写！但写又有什么用处？要从严就从严吧，我拒绝写，没有什么好写的！","index":21,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8bc90446ce"},{"id":"abf6bb20d0","type":"paragraph","text":"问：你写不写？","index":22,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8bc90446ce"},{"id":"f307ecf6ba","type":"paragraph","text":"答：干革命不能怕死！","index":23,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8bc90446ce"},{"id":"6419060e8f","type":"paragraph","text":"问：你希望从宽吗？也希望有出路吗？","index":24,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8bc90446ce"},{"id":"fd6afedd9c","type":"paragraph","text":"答：不希望。","index":25,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8bc90446ce"},{"id":"72a3ad8eee","type":"paragraph","text":"问：你上面的话是凭感情说出来的，还是凭理智说出来的？","index":26,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8bc90446ce"},{"id":"2c90b2db34","type":"paragraph","text":"答：是凭理智说出来的。","index":27,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8bc90446ce"},{"id":"3659949619","type":"paragraph","text":"……","index":28,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8bc90446ce"},{"id":"037386ef36","type":"paragraph","text":"问：你这一辈子什么时候最清醒？","index":29,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8bc90446ce"},{"id":"d1eeb7d76f","type":"paragraph","text":"答：从事情发生到现在这一段最清醒，因为我明白了真理。","index":30,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8bc90446ce"},{"id":"21a9f70a2f","type":"paragraph","text":"问：再问你一遍，什么时候最清醒？","index":31,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8bc90446ce"},{"id":"335dbd4b93","type":"paragraph","text":"答：我不改变说法，仍是现在再清醒。","index":32,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8bc90446ce"},{"id":"9c4bfb2946","type":"paragraph","text":"问：你有几个孩子？","index":33,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8bc90446ce"},{"id":"5f1ddccc18","type":"paragraph","text":"答：一个，是个女孩，我很喜欢她，照片寄来后，大家都说长得很好，又白又胖。","index":34,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8bc90446ce"},{"id":"b51b318fda","type":"paragraph","text":"问：难道你不为你的孩子，妻子，父母想一想吗？","index":35,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8bc90446ce"},{"id":"f8718ee430","type":"paragraph","text":"答：为了革命，我不能想那么多！","index":36,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8bc90446ce"},{"id":"dabb5e0f72","type":"paragraph","text":"问：你所说的革命是什么？","index":37,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8bc90446ce"},{"id":"5616908d17","type":"paragraph","text":"答：就是上面所谈的。","index":38,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8bc90446ce"},{"id":"8cf8450e31","type":"paragraph","text":"问：按公安六条衡量，你的行为是什么性质？","index":39,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8bc90446ce"},{"id":"2d3554e293","type":"paragraph","text":"答：按你们的公安六条，我的行为是反革命，但是我自己不那么认为。","index":40,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8bc90446ce"},{"id":"a348c7b58d","type":"paragraph","text":"问：你今天的态度好吗？","index":41,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8bc90446ce"},{"id":"4e0bea67e2","type":"paragraph","text":"答：好！好在我认清了真理。","index":42,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8bc90446ce"},{"id":"aa5d7cb0e7","type":"paragraph","text":"问：党的政策你知道吗？","index":43,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8bc90446ce"},{"id":"f32b58a940","type":"paragraph","text":"答：规定的是坦白从宽，抗拒从严，但是我认为我不必那样做！","index":44,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8bc90446ce"}],"page":{"id":"85ddb3dd21","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8bc90446ce","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}